title: Rooster's Head
provenance: Collection of Carol B. Brener and Stephen W. Brener
description: In the form of a rooster's head, with comb on top, stylized feathers, orange glass eyes, open beak, front and reverse sides identical. Thin, flat lid located at base and opened by squeezing the hinged, lower beak. Suspension ring attached to back of neck. Striker on lid bottom.
